{"tid":432524,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[失戀博物館] 致那些放得低或放唔低嘅人與關係","createTime":"2017-10-11T14:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T12:03:42.000Z","uid":82070,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dad66c9910370755e0e3ebcf3e2c07d35dbad99f","tid":432524,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-11T14:59:04.000Z","msg":"是咁的，一直以嚟我都有同唔少巴絲打傾感情問題<br />\n愈黎愈明白，感情事最難嘅唔係開始<br />\n而係放低 (又或者根本未開始就要放低)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以今晚嘅我，決定開一個網上版嘅失戀博物館<br />\n(現實版嘅係克羅地亞，相關文章可以睇呢度︰<a href=\"https://travelblog.expedia.com.hk/popular-travel-destinations/3854/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravelblog.expedia.com.hk%2Fpopular-travel-destinations%2F3854%2F&d=yPJiFznuub29aD1mpa7tk5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3ca675e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://travelblog.expedia.com.hk/popular-travel-destinations/3854/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n目的係希望讓過去嘅愛/關係/回憶得到可以安放嘅位置<br />\n因為我相信，過去不必遺忘，卻總需放下<br />\n然後，先可以為你嘅人生找尋新出路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n失戀博物館︰<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/OJy1aVI2X5dJITKV2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FOJy1aVI2X5dJITKV2&d=yPJiFznuub29aD1mpa7tk5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d0eb8abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/OJy1aVI2X5dJITKV2</a><br />\n<br />\n大家可以係上面留言/post展品<br />\n<br />\n步驟︰<br />\n1. 揀選一樣物品作代表(任何勾起回憶嘅定情信物、象徵物、感情遺物)<br />\n2. 影相<br />\n3. 上載作為展品<br />\n3. 留下你同佢嘅故事/你對呢段關係想嘅野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直接入tg group傾計︰<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/FzppmAxQzRTk1N3AtgXW6w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FFzppmAxQzRTk1N3AtgXW6w&d=yPJiFznuub29aD1mpa7tk5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c083404c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/FzppmAxQzRTk1N3AtgXW6w</a><br />\n<br />\n留意返︰<br />\n1. 由於要有upload相嘅功能，所以要登入google account，無gmail又唔想專登開嘅巴絲打，可以喺呢度post/直接tg我，由我代為upload<br />\n2. google form只係初步方便大家，之後失戀博物館有可能移師至網站展覽(初步諗緊同一啲機構合作借出網站區域，但只限NGO，唔會for商業機構/商業用途，放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n3. 如果決定上載相片、故事或留言，呢啲內容就有機會公開讓有緣人見到 (包括你既對象)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n4. 自己嘅故事自己拍︰故事有機會拍成短片，google form有得比你選擇參唔參與拍攝 (順便可以上workshop學下拍片)<br />\n5. 你可以唔拍自己，剩係拍人地嘅故仔，又或者調轉都得 (請列明)<br />\n<br />\n介紹住咁多先，有問題/意見留言話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e19dcc5a1750fe47369a74ab2e89c9c03683fc","tid":432524,"uid":143391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bad426c201e589556d85a26b5def326db5c6fa","tid":432524,"uid":137847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:18:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"307a0b3ee2e9342ba7864503b3e4b1dddbda6090","tid":432524,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T07:02:23.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27adfca8f9109c4cba17fba2bf79807fbf78abdf","tid":432524,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:35:11.000Z","msg":"group link已經修改為︰<br />\n<br />\n直接tg館主︰<a href=\"https://t.me/@Ching1165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2F%40Ching1165&d=yPJiFznuub29aD1mpa7tk5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e4e0d007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/@Ching1165</a>"},{"pid":"7e8ca1c40e59e375b8f2452cc696bec8bca8a003","tid":432524,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:37:43.000Z","msg":"分手寄賣店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926dcf70192d18312c3807e9b7d4fcc7bb8a9cdb","tid":432524,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:49:30.000Z","msg":"即使無特別咩物品，純粹想搵人傾下，都可以係google form留低你嘅故事，<br />\n館主會親自逐一回覆"},{"pid":"6bb262dcf3ce45d41538eca623e003d65e26b604","tid":432524,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:50:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分手寄賣店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n解憂雜貨店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536ff9f85e5b7239255f49b1f2ce1ab0a04d35cc","tid":432524,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T07:54:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇左幾個巴絲係google form打既故事<br />\n有啲眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261c9ad4155ba85bde75ce4cbf93acd9c04882cf","tid":432524,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T09:09:59.000Z","msg":"問世間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ded8e7b5264a23ecf00286aa26909fb27c19795","tid":432524,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T12:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問世間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n直教人.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}